cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

This paper discusses a problem related to image processing and proposes a solution using neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses different architecture designs and loss functions, which are related to machine learning and deep learning, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely categories as well. The paper also mentions convergence to solutions with smaller test errors, which is related to optimization, making cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) a possible category. Finally, the paper discusses modelling power, which is related to multimedia, making cs.MM (Multimedia) a less likely but still possible category.
